CWP Software Update: CWP/SU Release 32: 21 July 1998  (32th edition)

The CWP/SU: Seismic Un*x package is the world's most widely used
free seismic research and processing software environment.
There have been more than 1400 verified installs of SU in
50 countries worldwide.
