New codes:
================================================================
prestack finite-difference migration
prestack PSPI migration
prestack Fourier finite-difference migration
prestack split-step migration
3D  V(z) common offset inversion (migration) (beta version)
normalize traces by rms, median, or maximum in a time window
a new version of the 3D viewer
a newer version of the reflectivity modeling code
